				"description": "<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3f11a43f-7fff-b191-54ea-123cc847b929\"><strong>Variable Damage:</strong> Damage can be bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing, and can be treated as any metal (like silver or adamantine). </span></p>\n<p><strong>Penetrating:</strong> Deals double damage to objects.</p>"
